1) Directory ops contains scripts to be run by user. More information is given in  
 ops/README file.
 
2) Directory anal contains modules used by the above scripts to perform analysis.

3) Directory comm is empty for now.

4) Directory dbase contains modules and classes interacting with database.
 
5) Directory dev is not distributed in the AmonPy package distribution. It contains 
   development and/or outdated scripts and modules. It is available only in the respiratory
   for developers.
   
6) Directory sim contains modules for simulations used by the simulation script
   run_archival.py in ops.
   
7) Directory test contains testing scripts.

8) Directory tools contains various non-analysis modules (for plotting, time conversion,
   pop-up window creation etc.) used by the modules in other directories. 
      